{"id": 2888, "genre": 1001, "title": "你都有哪些独特的犒劳自己的方式？", "description": "赶完一个 deadline 就与世隔绝睡上8小时。", "record_count": 3174, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20190408170159xkBANRUsaCdEnDZz.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2019-04-17T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 339712, "content": "看美食电影🎬，然后自己做饭", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1523581}, {"id": 341504, "content": "在家放首歌，扭得难看点无所谓，蹦跶完吃个肉肉睡一觉", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1466083}, {"id": 339969, "content": "洗完澡睡大觉～", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1493701}, {"id": 340225, "content": "买个平时舍不得买的无用物品", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1641558}, {"id": 340481, "content": "大保健", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 674509}, {"id": 339714, "content": "喝杯咖啡", "image": null, "praise_count": 63, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1140282}, {"id": 339715, "content": "吃，不担心长胖的吃！买，不会破产的那种买！玩，第二天可以睡懒觉随意的看视频、玩游戏！", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1602254}, {"id": 339971, "content": "喝可乐", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1505226}, {"id": 340483, "content": "发呆", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1643164}, {"id": 339716, "content": "躺在床上刷剧放空自我", "image": null, "praise_count": 43, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1497228}, {"id": 339972, "content": "搞定项目后，团队庆功，烂醉一晚上", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1597162}, {"id": 339717, "content": "睡个天昏地暗。吃个天翻地覆。。。。这算么", "image": null, "praise_count": 18, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1640053}, {"id": 339973, "content": "摆弄一下花花草草，练一下尤克里里", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1640584}, {"id": 340485, "content": "打桌球", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1643163}, {"id": 339718, "content": "刷剧。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 749248}, {"id": 339974, "content": "狂吃狂睡", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1640589}, {"id": 340486, "content": "买花苗，种...", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1459943}, {"id": 339719, "content": "其实就是看看书\n摆弄一下自己的花花草草\n泡杯茶，喝杯咖啡\n逗逗狗，逗逗猫\n做顿好吃的或者吃个种草很久的好吃的\n感觉就超级棒了\n或者参加一个超火的活动\n\n总之就是让自己完全忘了不开心的事儿\n放松一下，给自己个空间，让自己真的松下来，不要绷着", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1625130}, {"id": 339975, "content": "躺尸看剧吃零食 爽极", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 920400}, {"id": 339720, "content": "对自己购物车里囤积已久的好物下手", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1518231}, {"id": 339976, "content": "躺尸", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1640594}, {"id": 339721, "content": "早上睡到自然醒，起床泡一桶酸菜泡面，配快乐肥宅水，加电影", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1640057}, {"id": 339977, "content": "买一个一直想买但是又没有买的东西", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1640599}, {"id": 340489, "content": "没有…", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1378753}, {"id": 339722, "content": "没课的下午午睡睡醒出去喝杯咖啡，精神焕发之后看场电影", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1467319}, {"id": 340234, "content": "就...关掉所有社交软件然后看书看剧吧，社交真的好累。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 664561}, {"id": 340490, "content": "躺着不干什么", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1610551}, {"id": 339723, "content": "看大哥大，笑到不能自我", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1635898}, {"id": 339979, "content": "犒劳自己的话，我真的很喜欢旅行，只有自己的那种。心情不好的时候可能才会在家里躺一整天什么都不想。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1640616}, {"id": 339724, "content": "准备考试，远离工作和人际关系", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1521452}, {"id": 339980, "content": "去外出爬山 给我妈妈买礼物", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1640618}, {"id": 339725, "content": "买玩具", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1231830}, {"id": 339726, "content": "逃掉不重要的课，推掉不重要的约会，把一整个的下午连着晚上的时间都送给自己", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1615725}, {"id": 340238, "content": "吃+看电影", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1640906}, {"id": 340494, "content": "想好好努力学习", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1643407}, {"id": 339727, "content": "吃顿自己想吃的", "image": "img/option/option/20190417115626tK1RC7Tfe2aUIPMX", "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1624003}, {"id": 339728, "content": "辞职", "image": null, "praise_count": 20, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1417126}, {"id": 339729, "content": "放空。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1438718}, {"id": 339985, "content": "通宵一手零食一手肥皂剧", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1359790}, {"id": 339730, "content": "心情好了，买东西犒劳自己；心情不好，买东西安慰自己；某项事情完成不错，买东西奖励自己；完成不好，买东西抚慰自己😂😂😂", "image": null, "praise_count": 77, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 419840}, {"id": 339986, "content": "扒一个草", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1611049}, {"id": 340242, "content": "打機 手邊有零食", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1562455}, {"id": 339731, "content": "练琴使我快乐", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1640088}, {"id": 339987, "content": "关机 睡觉", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1640631}, {"id": 339732, "content": "拉上窗帘打开推特....", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1334247}, {"id": 339988, "content": "听相声", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1639502}, {"id": 340244, "content": "看球赛", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1639730}, {"id": 339733, "content": "骑车或搭公交到处乱走", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1513860}, {"id": 339734, "content": "去海边跑步", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 298635}, {"id": 339735, "content": "学习使我快乐", "image": null, "praise_count": 35, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1451145}]}